Interface VuforiaTrackables

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Collection<VuforiaTrackable>, java.lang.Iterable<VuforiaTrackable>, java.util.List<VuforiaTrackable>

    public interface VuforiaTrackables
extends java.util.List<VuforiaTrackable>
    VuforiaTrackables represents a set of targets that can be visually tracked.
